Description:
	Roiling ink stains of unliving shadow - the Blot is a dark soul from the 
	deepest crevasses of the Umbral Plains.
	
	They lurk in the darkness and pass from place to place with a bouncing 
	motion. To attack they will leap through their victims, engulfing them in 
	shadow.